<C>__{joe}
<D>__{the un human development index ranks niger the number one least liveable country in the world. i started my foreign service there. as ambassador to gabon, i travelled back many times. then as director of africa policy for the nsc under president clinton, i frequently visited, often met with prime minister mayaki. i know the former foreign minister. i know the minister of mines.}
<C>__{mike}
